OL,3,CThink tank calls for homes to be built
OL,4,Cfor UK 'tax migrants'
OL,6,FGuernsey should build tower blocks for
OL,7,Fwealthy UK migrants, a local think
OL,8,Ftank suggests.
OL,10,FThe Guernsey Policy and Economic Group
OL,11,Fbelieves the island could capitalise
OL,12,Fon tax-driven migrants who want to
OL,13,Favoid possible tariff rises from the
OL,14,Fnew Labour administration.
OL,16,FThe Group states: "The arrival of a
OL,17,FLabour Government with a firm
OL,18,Fintention to raise UK taxes means that
OL,19,Fthe wealthier can preserve a lot more
OL,20,Fof their wealth by leaving the UK and
OL,21,Fheading here.
