OL,3,CThink tank calls for homes to be built
OL,4,Cfor UK 'tax migrants'
OL,6,F"These tax-driven migrants can
OL,7,Fgenerate a lot of tax revenue for
OL,8,FGuernsey. They will pay lots in
OL,9,Fproperty and income taxes and their
OL,10,Fwealth will improve the economy."
OL,12,FUnder current laws, only around 1,500
OL,13,Fproperties are available for those
OL,14,Fwith a British or Irish passport with
OL,15,Fthe right to work in the UK.
OL,17,FThese 'Open Market' properties carry a
OL,18,Fprice premium to attract high-net-
OL,19,Fworth individuals.
