OL,4,Cfor UK 'tax migrants'
OL,6,FDespite a lack of housing in Guernsey,
OL,7,Festate agent Stuart Leslie believes
OL,8,Fhigh-worth individuals will not occupy
OL,9,F'Local Market' homes.
OL,11,FHe explains: "I think there can be a
OL,12,Fslight negative connotation with
OL,13,Fpeople coming to the island.
OL,15,F"It's not always seen as a favourable
OL,16,Fthing, but this is a very restricted
OL,17,Fhousing market and (UK migrants) are
OL,18,Fbuying in the top tier of pricing."
