OL,3,CThink tank calls for homes to be built
OL,4,Cfor UK 'tax migrants'
OL,6,FWhile it remains to be seen what tax
OL,7,Fhikes UK Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,8,Fcould announce in her Autumn Budget,
OL,9,Fpeople in Guernsey are closely
OL,10,Ffollowing to see whether UK residents
OL,11,Fwill be incentivised to relocate.
OL,13,FTax expert Paul O'Neill said: "The
OL,14,Fheadlines in the UK are that there is
OL,15,Fgoing to be an increase in Capital
OL,16,FGains Tax.
