OL,3,CThink tank calls for homes to be built
OL,4,Cfor UK 'tax migrants'
OL,6,F"There may be an increase in Income
OL,7,FTax, changes to the pension regime and
OL,8,Falso there's been very well
OL,9,Fdocumented, proposed changes to the
OL,10,FInheritance Tax Scheme which may catch
OL,11,Fmore people in the future."
OL,13,FJo Goddard from Locate Guernsey, a
OL,14,Fcompany which helps people move to the
OL,15,Fisland, says they are receiving around
OL,16,Ffour calls a day from UK residents
OL,17,Fwhen the topic of wealth and Capital
OL,18,FGains Tax is mentioned.
